OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1781205078
OL,3,CMother of woman shot dead by dad in
OL,4,CTexas files complaint against US police
OL,6,FThe mother of a British woman shot
OL,7,Fdead by her father in Texas hours
OL,8,Fbefore she was due to fly home has
OL,9,Fsubmitted a formal complaint against a
OL,10,FUS police force.
OL,12,FLucy Harrison, 23, was staying with
OL,13,Fher father, Kris Harrison, and his
OL,14,Ffamily in the town of Prosper when she
OL,15,Fwas shot in the chest on 10 January
OL,16,F2025.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
