OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1781205078
OL,3,CMother of woman shot dead by dad in
OL,4,CTexas files complaint against US police
OL,6,FWhile a UK inquest recently ruled that
OL,7,Fthe young woman, from Warrington,
OL,8,FCheshire, was unlawfully killed, no
OL,9,Fone has been prosecuted in connection
OL,10,Fwith her death in the United States.
OL,12,FHer mother, Jane Coates, believes her
OL,13,Fex-husband should be held accountable
OL,14,Ffor Lucy's death after he escaped
OL,15,Fcharges in the US, claiming the
OL,16,FAmerican investigation "lacked rigour"
OL,17,Fand "fell below professional
OL,18,Fstandards."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1781205078
OL,3,CMother of woman shot dead by dad in
OL,4,CTexas files complaint against US police
OL,6,FShe has now confirmed a formal
OL,7,Fcomplaint has been submitted directly
OL,8,Fto the Prosper Police Department in
OL,9,FTexas, demanding a full review of how
OL,10,Fthe case was handled.
OL,12,F"At the very core, this is not about
OL,13,Flaws or jurisdiction," she said in a
OL,14,Fstatement on a social media page set
OL,15,Fup in memory of her daughter.
OL,17,F"It is my strongly held belief that
OL,18,Fthis is about a police investigation
OL,19,Fwhich lacked rigour, scrutiny and fell
OL,20,Fbelow the professional standards Lucy
OL,21,Fdeserved.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1781205078
OL,3,CMother of woman shot dead by dad in
OL,4,CTexas files complaint against US police
OL,6,F"You will see on the second photo I
OL,7,Fhave posted, a chart which shows the
OL,8,Fdifferences between policing standards
OL,9,Fand procedures, making comparisons
OL,10,Fbetween the UK, US federal level and
OL,11,FTexas.
OL,13,F"Whilst the UK appears to have all the
OL,14,Fticks, we know only too well how at
OL,15,Ftimes, systems in the UK have let
OL,16,Fvictims and families down. It is by no
OL,17,Fmeans perfect."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1781205078
OL,3,CMother of woman shot dead by dad in
OL,4,CTexas files complaint against US police
OL,6,FShe added: "I have followed the
OL,7,Fdevastating murders of Ian Coates,
OL,8,FBarnaby Webber and Grace O'Malley-
OL,9,FKumar and have watched the incredible
OL,10,Ffamilies fight for truth, transparency
OL,11,Fand accountability during the public
OL,12,Finquiry.
OL,14,F"Even when the 'ticks' are in place,
OL,15,Ffamilies still have to fight for
OL,16,Faccountability, regardless of
OL,17,Fcountries and laws."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
