PN,39806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1781205078
OL,3,CMother of woman shot dead by dad in
OL,4,CTexas files complaint against US police
OL,6,FAt an inquest into Lucy's death at
OL,7,FCheshire Coroner's Court, Senior
OL,8,FCoroner Jacqueline Devonish ruled she
OL,9,Fdied due to unlawful killing on the
OL,10,Fgrounds of gross negligence
OL,11,Fmanslaughter.
OL,13,FConcluding, Ms Devonish said: "To
OL,14,Fshoot her through the chest whilst she
OL,15,Fwas standing would have required him
OL,16,Fto have been pointing the gun at his
OL,17,Fdaughter, without checking for
OL,18,Fbullets, and pulling the trigger.
OL,20,F"I find these actions to be reckless."
OL,26,@uD@_OU|D@AOU|D@fO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
