PN,39807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1781205078
OL,3,CMother of woman shot dead by dad in
OL,4,CTexas files complaint against US police
OL,6,FKris Harrison, described by the
OL,7,Fcoroner as a functioning alcoholic,
OL,8,Fclaimed the gun had gone off
OL,9,Faccidentally following a "big"
OL,10,Fargument about US President Donald
OL,11,FTrump while she was staying at his
OL,12,Fhome.
OL,14,FHe did not attend the inquest, but
OL,15,Fsaid in a statement that he had a
OL,16,Fconversation about guns with his
OL,17,Fdaughter, and she asked to see the
OL,18,Fgun, having never discussed his gun
OL,19,Fownership with him before.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
